Package org.eclipse.collections.impl.map

package org.eclipse.collections.impl.map
This package contains implementations of the MapIterable interface.

A MapIterable contains read-only Map API, with the minor exception inherited from java.lang.Iterable.

This package contains the following implementations:

  • AbstractSynchronizedMapIterable - a synchronized view of a map.
